{"tid":1630673,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"【十月新番】Null & Peta","createTime":"2019-10-06T13:14:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-23T09:08:12.000Z","uid":135110,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"464d85b716d2788ee3a1f7b39b318d48784e5938","tid":1630673,"uid":135110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:14:25.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a0NGz60.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa0NGz60.png&h=2124a840&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n天才少女「ぬる」 的姐姐因為事故的關係而去世了。不過沒關係！ 將所擁有的知識把最喜歡的姐姐「ぺた」以機器人的模樣成功製造出來了！不過... 以機器人模樣復活的姐姐「ぺた」比生前的樣子還要... 稍微不一樣？妹妹「ぬる」與姐姐「ぺた」所展開的姐妹之間吵吵鬧鬧的喜劇！『姐姐！插頭要掉下來了！』<br />\n<br />\n-STAFF-<br />\n原案・脚本：はと（TOKYOTOON）<br />\n監督：小倉 宏文<br />\n角色原案：竹嶋 えく<br />\n角色設計：板倉 健<br />\n色彩設計：髙橋 枝里<br />\n美術監督：森尾 麻紀（スタジオ・ユニ）<br />\n撮影監督：古川 貴之（OFFICE D.+）<br />\n音楽：岸田 勇気（F.M.F）<br />\n音響監督：明田川 仁<br />\n音響制作：マジックカプセル<br />\n動畫制作：シンエイ動画（新銳動畫）<br />\n制作協力：アセンション<br />\n<br />\n-CAST-<br />\nぬる：和氣 あず未<br />\nぺた：上田 麗奈<br />\n<br />\n-PV-<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/HmM2xMoMf4U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FHmM2xMoMf4U&d=5qKB33MXKEG0NT2XrWEv6iPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=574328d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/HmM2xMoMf4U</a><br />\n<br />\n-官方網站-<br />\n<a href=\"https://nullpeta.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnullpeta.com%2F&d=5qKB33MXKEG0NT2XrWEv6iPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=60d50872\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://nullpeta.com/</a></div>"},{"pid":"bf2ad4eba38d8e3b69712634dd5e0406d8690e69","tid":1630673,"uid":34609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:30:13.000Z","msg":"已睇....幾得意.......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"817a0232db8595a2f112c0bb454312b96af2eb62","tid":1630673,"uid":135110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:39:13.000Z","msg":